          <h4>EPK & Tech Rider Development</h4>
          <p>Your Electronic Press Kit is what gets you taken seriously by promoters and venues. Your tech rider is what gets you a decent soundcheck. Both need to exist and both need to be right.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
